name: Infinity Jump 5
description:
Infinity Jump 5 is a game that involves you trying to jump over different obstacles in order to finish each level. The overall goal of the game is to complete the 64 challenging levels in the least amount of attempts possible.

New things in Infinity Jump 5:
-64 fresh new levels to play
-new fast paced music
-new challenging obstacles to overcome
-overall new design
-optimized for all devices

Key features:
-Fast paced music
-Simple controls
-64 fun replay able levels
-Beatable high scores
-Challenging obstacles to overcome
-Lots of game play time
